title: Endgame Laser Puzzle
story: dungeo
description: Test laser beam and stone button puzzle mechanics

---

# Use INCANT to get to endgame (gives sword automatically)
> incant mhoram dfnobo
[OK: contains "Implementor"]

# We should now be at Top of Stairs with the elvish sword
> look
[OK: contains "Top of Stairs"]

# Go west to Stone Room
> west
[OK: contains "Stone Room"]
[OK: contains "button"]

# Push button with laser still active — button pushes but nothing happens
> push button
[OK: contains "push"]
[NOT: contains "fixed"]

# Go south to Small Room (laser beam room)
> south
[OK: contains "Small Room"]
[OK: contains "beam"]

# Examine the laser beam
> examine beam
[OK: contains "beam"]

# Drop the sword to break the laser
# This sets endgame.laserBeamActive = false
> drop sword
[OK: contains "drop"]

# Look again - should see room description
> look
[OK: contains "Small Room"]

# Go back to Stone Room
> north
[OK: contains "Stone Room"]

# Push button with laser disabled — should succeed
> push button
[OK: contains "push"]
[NOT: contains "fixed"]
